{
  "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "给你一个多边形，再给一个点，它到底在里面还是外面？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "对人眼很直观，可计算机没有眼睛，得靠一条明确的规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "数学家想出两种漂亮的办法：射线法和环绕数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "ray",
      "line_id": "ray-1",
      "filename": "ray-ray-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/ray-ray-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "从这个点向右画一条射线，一直伸到无穷远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "ray",
      "line_id": "ray-2",
      "filename": "ray-ray-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/ray-ray-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.36,
      "size": 21744,
      "text": "数一数它穿过了多边形的几条边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "ray",
      "line_id": "ray-3",
      "filename": "ray-ray-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/ray-ray-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "穿越奇数次说明点在里面，偶数次则在外面，这叫偶奇规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "winding",
      "line_id": "wind-1",
      "filename": "winding-wind-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/winding-wind-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "换个视角：站在这个点上，盯着边界走一圈。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "winding",
      "line_id": "wind-2",
      "filename": "winding-wind-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/winding-wind-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "边界绕着你转了几整圈，这个整数就是环绕数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "winding",
      "line_id": "wind-3",
      "filename": "winding-wind-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/winding-wind-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "环绕数不为零就在里面，为零就在外面，这叫非零规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "concave",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "concave-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/concave-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "对凸多边形，两种规则永远给出相同答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "concave",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "concave-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/concave-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "可一旦多边形自己交叉，比如一笔画成的五角星，就不一样了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "concave",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "concave-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/concave-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "星星中心被绕了两圈，非零规则算它在内，偶奇规则却算它在外。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "切换不同多边形，看采样点被染成里外两种样子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "再切换规则，观察五角星的星芯如何在两法之间反转结论。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "射线法数交点奇偶，环绕数看旋转圈数，都能判定内外。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "它们撑起了游戏碰撞、地图落区和图形填充的底层判断。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "point-in-polygon",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/point-in-polygon/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "同一个问题，两种视角，希望你也爱上这份严谨，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 34.24,
  "total_size": 547776
}